%N A395656 Expansion of 1/(9*x) * (1/(4-3*g)^3 - 1), where g = 1+x*g^4 is the g.f. of A002293.
%F A395656 a(n) = A395659(n)/(n+1) = (1/(n+1)) * Sum_{k=0..n} 3^k * binomial(k+3,3) * binomial(4*n+4,n-k).
